org.cpsolver.ifs.extension

Class Extension<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.extension.Extension<V,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Variable
    T - Value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelListener<V,T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConflictStatistics, ExtensionWithContext, ViolatedInitials

    public class Extension<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
extends Object
implements ModelListener<V,T>
    Generic extension of IFS solver.

    All extensions should extend this class.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
